                <div class="large-8 large-offset-2 columns">
                <h4 id="project-name"> IDEA REDESIGN</h4>
                <p>IDEA is Northeastern University’s student led and operated venture accelerator. The organization provides a variety of resources to Northeastern affiliated entrepreneurs looking to start their own businesses. Through the “Ready, Set, Go” stage-gate process, IDEA provides ventures with coaches, mentors, business planning resources, and the ability to apply for gap funding. </p>
                <p>As a studio member at Scout I was the lead developer on the project, aiding the design team in critiques on user experience and coding a completely custom mobile-ready WordPress theme. As the Creative Officer at IDEA, I was tasked with revisiting the organization’s branding and refresh it side-by-side with the development of the new website.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="project">
