                <img src="../img/projects/idea_website/idea_patterns.png">
            </div>
            <hr>
        </div>
    </section>

        <section class="project">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="large-8 large-offset-2 columns">
                <p>On the development side, I worked on building the custom WordPress theme that would later be handed over to the IDEA team so that they could easily maintain and update their site. Working closely with my teammates at Scout on the project, I was able to build in featured posts, easy-to-create team member profiles, and many other functions that helped the website feel dynamic and polished. Along with this, I used Advanced Custom Fields to make an easily digestible WordPress back-end to help maintain the site's content.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

